{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1160,"text":"I design engineering projects"},{"time":2920,"text":"for middle school\nand high school students,"},{"time":5280,"text":"often using materials\nthat are pretty unexpected."},{"time":9000,"text":"My inspiration comes\nfrom problems in my daily life."},{"time":12880,"text":"For example,"},{"time":14120,"text":"one time I needed a costume\nto go to a comic convention,"},{"time":18160,"text":"but I didn't want to spend too much money,"},{"time":20240,"text":"so I made my own ..."},{"time":22800,"text":"with a light-up crown and skirt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26640,"text":"Another time,"},{"time":27880,"text":"I was devastated\nbecause my favorite mobile game,"},{"time":31840,"text":"Flappy Bird,"},{"time":33080,"text":"was being taken off the app store."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36840,"text":"So I was faced with the dilemma"},{"time":38400,"text":"to either never update my phone\nor never play Flappy Bird again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":45240,"text":"Unhappy with both options,"},{"time":47280,"text":"I did the only thing\nthat made sense to me."},{"time":49840,"text":"I made a physical version of Flappy Bird"},{"time":52040,"text":"that could never be\ntaken off the app store."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":57120,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":62280,"text":"(Beeping)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":65080,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"So a few of my friends\nwere also pretty addicted to the game,"},{"time":72280,"text":"and I invited them to play as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74960,"text":"(Video) Friend: Ah!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"(Video) Friend: What the heck?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":81680,"text":"And they told me that it was\njust as infuriating as the original game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87040,"text":"So I uploaded a demo\nof this project online,"},{"time":90440,"text":"and to my surprise it went viral."},{"time":92960,"text":"It had over two million views\nin just a few days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":96080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":97520,"text":"And what's more interesting\nare people's comments."},{"time":100760,"text":"A lot of people\nwanted to make it their own,"},{"time":103200,"text":"or asked me how it was made."},{"time":105080,"text":"So this kind of confirmed my idea\nthat through a creative project,"},{"time":109400,"text":"we can teach people about engineering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112440,"text":"With the money made from the viral video,"},{"time":114600,"text":"we were able to let students\nin our classroom"},{"time":116880,"text":"all make their own game in a box."},{"time":119560,"text":"Although it was pretty challenging,"},{"time":121440,"text":"they learned a lot of new concepts\nin engineering and programming."},{"time":125160,"text":"And they were all eager to learn\nso they could finish the game as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":130440,"text":"So before Flappy Bird Box,"},{"time":133080,"text":"I had the idea of using creative\nengineering projects to teach students."},{"time":138640,"text":"When I was teaching at a middle school,"},{"time":140920,"text":"we asked our students to build a robot\nfrom a standard technology kit."},{"time":145760,"text":"And I noticed that\na lot of them seemed bored."},{"time":148680,"text":"Then a few of them\nstarted taking pieces of paper"},{"time":151480,"text":"and decorating their robots."},{"time":153120,"text":"And then more of them got into it,"},{"time":155080,"text":"and they became\nmore interested in the project."},{"time":157720,"text":"So I started looking\nfor more creative ways"},{"time":160640,"text":"to introduce technology to students."},{"time":163560,"text":"What I found was that most technology kits\navailable in school"},{"time":167720,"text":"look a little intimidating."},{"time":169600,"text":"They're all made of plastic parts\nthat you can't customize."},{"time":173560,"text":"On top of that,\nthey're all very expensive,"},{"time":176200,"text":"costing hundreds of dollars per kit."},{"time":178680,"text":"So that's certainly not very affordable\nfor most classroom budgets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183320,"text":"Since I didn't find anything,"},{"time":184800,"text":"I decided to make something on my own."},{"time":187040,"text":"I started with paper and fabric."},{"time":190000,"text":"After all, we all played\nwith those since we were kids,"},{"time":193200,"text":"and they are also pretty cheap"},{"time":194760,"text":"and can be found\nanywhere around the house."},{"time":198200,"text":"And I prototyped a project"},{"time":199920,"text":"where students\ncan create a light-up creature"},{"time":202520,"text":"using fabric and googly eyes."},{"time":205040,"text":"They were all helping\neach other in classrooms,"},{"time":207280,"text":"and were laughing\nand discussing the project."},{"time":209720,"text":"And most importantly,"},{"time":210960,"text":"they were able to insert\ntheir own creativity into the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214680,"text":"So because of the success of this project,"},{"time":216760,"text":"I continued to create\nmore engineering projects"},{"time":219480,"text":"to challenge my students."},{"time":221360,"text":"And I also started to take\nthese workshops outside of school"},{"time":225280,"text":"and into the community."},{"time":226840,"text":"And something really interesting happened."},{"time":229200,"text":"I noticed a lot of people\nfrom very diverse backgrounds"},{"time":232240,"text":"started coming to our workshops."},{"time":234640,"text":"And specifically,"},{"time":236040,"text":"there were a lot more women\nand minorities than I expected,"},{"time":240920,"text":"and that you wouldn't usually see\nat a traditional engineering workshop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245280,"text":"Now take a look at this employee report\nat a major technology company in 2016."},{"time":251200,"text":"Women make up only 19 percent\nof the technology workforce."},{"time":255280,"text":"And underrepresented minorities\nmake up only four percent."},{"time":259440,"text":"This statistic might look familiar"},{"time":261519,"text":"if you walked into\na high school robotics club,"},{"time":265080,"text":"or a college engineering class."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267720,"text":"Now, there's a wide variety of problems"},{"time":272040,"text":"that contribute to the lack of diversity\nin the technology force."},{"time":276440,"text":"Perhaps one solution could be"},{"time":278520,"text":"to introduce technology to students\nthrough creative projects."},{"time":283880,"text":"I'm not saying that this\ncould solve everything,"},{"time":287040,"text":"but it could introduce technology"},{"time":290240,"text":"to people who originally\nwouldn't be interested in it"},{"time":292920,"text":"because of how it has been\nportrayed and taught in school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296760,"text":"So how do we start to change\nthe perception of technology?"},{"time":301920,"text":"Most students think\nthat it's boring or unwelcoming,"},{"time":306560,"text":"so I have always designed projects\nfollowing three principles."},{"time":310360,"text":"First is having a low floor,"},{"time":312880,"text":"and that means this project\nis easy to get started."},{"time":317080,"text":"So take a look at this tutorial."},{"time":319880,"text":"The first project\nwe asked students to learn"},{"time":322000,"text":"is to make a circuit on paper."},{"time":324120,"text":"As you can see, it doesn't\ntake very long to learn,"},{"time":326640,"text":"and it's pretty easy even for beginners."},{"time":329800,"text":"And having a low floor also means\nthat we're removing the financial barrier"},{"time":334440,"text":"that prevents people\nfrom completing a project."},{"time":337480,"text":"So with paper, copper tape,\nlightbulb and a battery,"},{"time":341360,"text":"people can complete this project\nfor under a dollar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345280,"text":"So second principle\nis having a high ceiling."},{"time":348760,"text":"This means that there's\na lot of room to grow,"},{"time":351840,"text":"and students are\nconstantly being challenged."},{"time":355400,"text":"At first it might just be\na light-up creature,"},{"time":358000,"text":"but then you can add sensors\nand microcontrollers,"},{"time":360840,"text":"and start to program the creature\nto interact with its environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"And finally,"},{"time":367360,"text":"the third principle is customization."},{"time":369840,"text":"This means that we can make\nthis project relevant to anyone."},{"time":374880,"text":"That's the beauty\nof using everyday materials;"},{"time":377400,"text":"it's very easy to customize\nusing paper and fabric."},{"time":381160,"text":"So even if you don't like Flappy Bird,"},{"time":384360,"text":"you can still make your own game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387440,"text":"(Video) Student: So our game\nis about Justin Bieber,"},{"time":389920,"text":"because he's been speeding,"},{"time":392640,"text":"and the object is to prevent him\nfrom getting caught by the LAPD --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":400000,"text":"(Video) Student:\nYeah, but he's changing so --"},{"time":402200,"text":"we're a part of his posse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":407720,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}